OL,4,CGrammy Awards scrap controversial
OL,5,Cvoting committees
OL,6, The organisers of the Grammy Awards
OL,7, have scrapped their anonymous voting
OL,8, committees following allegations of
OL,9, rigging, favouritism and racism.
OL,11,FThe Recording Academy said its voting
OL,12,Fmembers - which run into thousands -
OL,13,Fwould instead select next year's
OL,14,Fnominations and winners.
OL,16,FStars such as Zayn Malik and Halsey had
OL,17,Fclaimed the selection process was
OL,18,Funfair and lacked transparency.
OL,20,FArtists of colour have long-criticised
OL,21,Fthe awards for a lack of diversity.
